{
  "text": "Cell necrosis was determined with LDH release using CytoTox-ONE LDH leakage assay as described previously [CITATION_1] . In brief, the cell culture medium at different time points was transferred to a black fluorescence plate and incubated for 10 minutes with CytoTox-ONE reagent followed by stop solution. Fluorescence was measured at 560 nm.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "17273639"
